      "message": "super nit: Is it safe to |release| a pointer that is no longer pointing to a valid object? In the odd scenario where the async run happens to run after the condition check but before this statement, you\u0027d have that situation.\n\n- I *think* it\u0027s safe.\n- This situation is extremely unlikely.",
